biotools.summary:
incremental decision trees for prediction of Adenosine to Inosine RNA editing sites.

This repository contains datasets for the paper titled "Incremental Decision Trees for Prediction of Adenosine to Inosine RNA Editing Sites".

All Features.csv - Benchmark Dataset After Feature Extraction.

Enter the query RNA sequences here Predict Clear.

Selected Features.csv - Benchmark Dataset After Feature Selection.

Insert RNA string of any length.
